strong>WordPress Achievements</strong> plugin for your arcade site. Attract more users and keep the current users on your site with  <a title=\"WordPress Achievements Plugin\" href=\"http://exells.com/shop/users/wpachievements/\" target=\"_blank\">WPAchievements</a>. Create and manage achievements and ranks with ease.</p>\n<p>WPAchievements allows you creating of unlimited number of achievements. For each achievement you can select or upload an image. The plugin supports a lot of pre-configured user events which you can link to achievements. This enables you to reward your users for being active on your WP Arcade Site.</p>\n<p>Take a look at this short video that shows WPAchievements in action:</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe width=\"425\" height=\"344\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/jwD90GfapUY?wmode=transparent\" frameborder=\"0\" allowFullScreen> </iframe></p>\n<p><a title=\"WordPress Achievements\" href=\"http://exells.com/shop/users/wpachievements/\" target=\"_blank\">WPAchievements</a> backend:</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe width=\"425\" height=\"344\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/-5h2_Xmqw54?wmode=transparent\" frameborder=\"0\" allowFullScreen> </iframe></p>\n<p>Here is a list of included events triggers that are associated:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>MyArcadePlugin\n<ul>\n<li>Playing a game</li>\n<li>Adding a new game</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>MyScoresPresenter\n<ul>\n<li>Submitting a score</li>\n<li>Getting a highscore</li>\n<li>Earning a medal</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>MyArcadeContest\n<ul>\n<li>Taking part in a contest</li>\n<li>Winning a prize in a contest</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>BuddyPress\n<ul>\n<li>Uploading an avatar</li>\n<li>Posting updates</li>\n<li>Adding friends</li>\n<li>Giving gifts</li>\n<li>Creating groups</li>\n<li>Sending messages</li>\n<li>many many more&#8230;</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>WP Favorite Posts\n<ul>\n<li>Favoriting a game / post</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>bbPress events</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Get your copy of WPAchievements Plugin on <a title=\"Buy and Sell digital goods\" href=\"http://exells.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Exells &#8211; Your Virtual Marketplace</a>.</p>\n\n<!-- google_ad_section_end -->\n<p>Related posts:</p><ol>\n<li><a href=\'http://myarcadeplugin.com/updated-myarcadeplugin-fungames-myscorespresenter/\' rel=\'bookmark\' title=\'Updated: MyArcadePlugin, FunGames, MyScoresPresenter\'>Updated: MyArcadePlugin, FunGames, MyScoresPresenter</a></li>\n<li><a href=\'http://myarcadeplugin.com/arcade-contests-tournaments-with-myarcadecontest-plugin/\' rel=\'bookmark\' title=\'Arcade Contests / Tournaments with MyArcadeContest Plugin\'>Arcade Contests / Tournaments with MyArcadeContest Plugin</a></li>\n<li><a href=\'http://myarcadeplugin.com/free-wp-arcade-theme-buddypress-arcade/\' rel=\'bookmark\' title=\'Free WP Arcade Theme: BuddyPress Arcade\'>Free WP Arcade Theme: BuddyPress Arcade</a></li>\n</ol>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:81:\"http://myarcadeplugin.com/add-achievements-to-your-wp-arcade-site-with-ease/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:59:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n			\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:41:\"Septmber Affiliate Payments sent – 2012\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i: