these users to help them promoting their hard work. MyArcadeFeed allows you to create a XML list of selected games and offer a XML Games Feed service like Kongregate, Mochi, Playtomi, [...]\nRelated posts:<ol>\n<li><a href=\'http://myarcadeplugin.com/how-to-create-automated-online-games-website/\' rel=\'bookmark\' title=\'Create a 100% automated online games website\'>Create a 100% automated online games website</a></li>\n</ol>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Daniel\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3021:\"\n<!-- google_ad_section_start -->\n<p>We know that a lot of game developers are using MyArcadePlugin to present and promote their own games. Thereby we have developed a new plugin especially for these users to help them promoting their hard work.</p>\n<p><strong><a title=\"MyArcadeFeed\" href=\"http://exells.com/shop/arcade-plugins/myarcadefeed/\" target=\"_blank\">MyArcadeFeed</a></strong> allows you to create a XML list of selected games and offer a <strong>XML Games Feed</strong> service like Kongregate, Mochi, Playtomi, Scirra and other game distributors. Offering own game distribution service will help you to promote your games. Game Feeds generated with MyArcadeFeed can be fetched with <strong>MyArcadePlugin 5.60</strong> and above automatically or from any other <strong>Arcade Script</strong>.</p>\n<p><a title=\"MyAarcadeFeed\" href=\"http://exells.com/shop/arcade-plugins/myarcadefeed/\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1382\" title=\"MyArcadeFeed - Create own XML Game Feed\" src=\"http://myarcadeplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/myarcadefeed.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>MyArcadeFeed will generate a XML feed with following fields:</p>\n<table cellspacing=\"5\" cellpadding=\"5\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Field</th>\n<th>Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>id</td>\n<td>Unique ID for this game</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>name</td>\n<td>The name of this game</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>gameurl</td>\n<td>Post permalink of this game</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>gamecode</td>\n<td>The SWF file URL to use when adding this game on your website</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>category</td>\n<td>The category of the game</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>date</td>\n<td>The date this game was originally uploaded to the arcade.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>description</td>\n<td>A detailed description of the game</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>instructions</td>\n<td>Short instructions for the game written by the author of the game</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>width</td>\n<td>Width (in pixels) of the game</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>height</td>\n<td>Height (in pixels) of the game</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>thumbnail</td>\n<td>Thumbnail URL of the game (usually 100x100px)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>screenshot_1</td>\n<td>Screenshot 1 URL of the game. FALSE if no screenshot available</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>screenshot_2</td>\n<td>Screenshot 2 URL of the game. FALSE if no screenshot available</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>screenshot_3</td>\n<td>Screenshot 3 URL of the game. FALSE if no screenshot available</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>screenshot_4</td>\n<td>Screenshot 4 URL of the game. FALSE if no screenshot available</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Get MyArcadeFeed directly from <a title=\"Exells - Marketplace for digital goods\" href=\"http://exells.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Exells Marketplace</a>.</p>\n\n<!-- google_ad_section_end -->\n<p>Related posts:</p><ol>\n<li><a href=\'http://myarcadeplugin.com/how-to-create-automated-online-games-website/\' rel=\'bookmark\' title=\'Create a 100% automated online games website\'>Create a 100% automated online games website</a></li>\n</ol>\"