WP Arcade Theme</strong> has been updated with a lot of new features. Three new color schemes (Pink, Purple and Orange) and three new index page presentations (Miniclip Style, Full Width and Half Width) have been added.</p>\n<p>Furthermore, we have made ArcadeFlex compatible with BuddyPress and a blog template has been implemented.</p>\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\n<p>Now, this <strong>WP Arcade Theme</strong> has:<br />\n<span id=\"more-631\"></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>9 unique main colors (red, blue, green, brown, gray, black, purple, orange, pink)</li>\n<li>9 unique sidebar colors (red, blue, green, brown, gray, black, purple, orange, pink)</li>\n<li>4 front page modes (Default, Full Width, Half Width, Miniclip Style)</li>\n<li>2 sidebar positions (left, right)</li>\n<li>2 sliders (FlashSlider, NivoSlider)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>You will have the possibility to create over <strong>1296 unique combinations</strong> for your site (9 * 9 * 4 * 2 * 2)!</p>\n<p>Let&#8217;s take a look to the complete changelog of ArcadeFlex v1.40:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: 3 additional color schemes: pink, purple, orange</li>\n<li>New: 3 additional index page presentations: Full Width, Half Width, Miniclip Style</li>\n<li>New: MyArcadeContest archive contest template</li>\n<li>New: Buddypress theme support</li>\n<li>New: Advertisement Banner for the Blog View</li>\n<li>New: Blog Template</li>\n<li>New: Blog Archive Template</li>\n<li>New: Added do_action calls on 404, index and archive pages for custom hooks</li>\n<li>New: Support for &#8220;WP SEO Content Mananger&#8221; plugin</li>\n<li>New: Styling for the Leaderboard Widget</li>\n<li>New: More configurations settings to manage the slider</li>\n<li>New: Option to deactivate Cufon font</li>\n<li>Fix: Update of text descriptions of the backend</li>\n<li>Fix: Improved Query for slider pictures</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a title=\"ArcadeFlex Download\" href=\"http://exells.com/shop/arcade-themes/arcadeflex/\">Download ArcadeFlex</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{